Language: <F P=105> Arabic </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Cairo, 1 Feb (MENA)--An official at the Palestinian 
Information Office in Cairo has said that the Palestinians have 
held contacts with the Israelis to fix a date and venue [as 
received] for the meeting that the two sides had agreed during 
the Davos talks to hold in Cairo. This meeting is supposed to 
prepare the way for the upcoming talks in Cairo between Yasir 
