<F P=100> ARABIAN PENINSULA </F>
<F P=101> Kuwait </F>
<H3> <TI>   Afghan Envoy Arrives With Message for Amir </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  LD2901162694 Kuwait KUNA in Arabic 1340 GMT 29 Jan 94 </F>
<F P=103> LD2901162694 </F>
<F P=104>  Kuwait KUNA </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Arabic </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Kuwait, 29 Jan, KUNA -- Muhammad Sediq Jakari, the 
Afghan president's envoy and the delegation accompanying him, 
arrived here today in order to convey a message from President 
Borhanoddin Rabbani for Shaykh Jabir al-Ahmad al-Sabah, the amir 
of the State of Kuwait. 
  'Abd-al-'Aziz al-Dakhil, the Kuwaiti minister of state for 
cabinet affairs, welcomed him at the airport. 

</TEXT>

