Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Once again, two more foreign reporters, working for 
ABC, the Australian Broadcasting Corporation, were the victims 
of an attack in the Casbah quarter of Algiers. A statement by 
the security services has disclosed that the two reporters were 
taken to the hospital where one of them, a French national, died 
