<F P=102>  LD0102232394 Algiers Radio Algiers Network in Arabic 2200 
GMT 1 Feb 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD0102232394 </F>
<F P=104>  Algiers Radio Algiers Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Arabic </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Excerpts] In a statement issued today, the Ministry of 
Communications strongly condemned the cowardly assassination 
that has recently grieved the entire community of journalists 
overseas and considers it as a practice alien to Algeria's 
traditions. [passage omitted]: 
  The statement made clear that the two reporters went to the 
Casbah quarter without taking into consideration the 
instructions of the authorities. It added that a police patrol 
had come across them yesterday at Bab El Oued and advised them 
not to go to some areas without taking the necessary precautions. 
  The two reporters who came to Algeria to cover the national 
conference wanted to complete their work by doing some field 
investigations. [passage omitted] 

</TEXT>

