<H3> <TI>   Two New Palestinian Papers To Be Launched </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  TA0102140894 Jerusalem Israel Television Channel 1 Network 
in Arabic 1700 GMT 31 Jan 94 </F>

<F P=103> TA0102140894 </F>
<F P=104>  Jerusalem Israel Television Channel 1 Network 
in Arabic 1700 GMT 31 Jan 94 </F>



<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105>Arabic </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Palestinian sources in Amman have stated that two 
newspapers will be launched shortly in the West Bank. The first 
one, to be published in English, will be called JERUSALEM TIMES. 
It will be edited by Hanna Sinyurah, former editor of AL-FAJR, 
