Article Type:BFN 

<F P=106> [Exclusive] </F>
  [Text] In a story totally different from the official story 
announced earlier by Damascus about the death of Basil al-Asad, 
eldest son of Syrian President Hafiz al-Asad, highly reliable 
sources have emphasized that Basil was the target of an armed 
attack on Wednesday, 19 January 1994, during a visit to Beirut. 
  Following the attack, Basil was moved to a Syrian Hospital 
