<H3> <TI>   Nine Soldiers, 6 Kashmiris Reportedly Killed </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  BK0102150694 Islamabad PTV Television Network in English 
1400 GMT 1 Feb 94 </F>

<F P=103> BK0102150694 </F>
<F P=104>  Islamabad PTV Television Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> English </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] In occupied Kashmir, mojahedin have intensified 
their attacks on Indian forces in retaliation to the atrocities 
committed against Kashmiri people. Mojahedin attacked military 
installations in Badgam, Srinagar, Anantnag-Islamabad, and 
Rajaori area killing seven Indian soldiers and wounding several 
others. In Bijbiara, mojahedin clashed with the rampaging 
soldiers killing two of them and wounding a number of them. 
Another report says Indian soldiers during their siege and 
search operations have martyred six more innocent Kashmiris in 
Srinagar, Bijbiara, Kupwara, and Pampur. 

</TEXT>

