Language: <F P=105> Arabic </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Yusuf Bin-'Alawi Bin-'Abdallah, Oman's minister of 
state for foreign affairs, today arrived in Amman on a brief 
visit to Jordan during which he will relay an oral message to 
His Majesty King Husayn from his brother Sultan Qabus Bin-Sa'id 
