<H3> <TI>   IRNA Announces Maiden Issue of Publication </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  NC3101133794 Tehran ABRAR in Persian 23 Jan 94 p 3 </F>
<F P=103> NC3101133794 </F>
<F P=104>  Tehran ABRAR </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Persian </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] The first issue of the publication "JOURNAL OF 
EVENTS" [DAFTAR-E RU'YDADHA] on art, literature, and culture 
published by the Cultural Review Committee of IRNA has been 
disseminated. 
  In the first edition of this monthly magazine a variety of 
articles of cultural interest have been included, such as: the 
Farsi language, books, publications, the theater, music, 
sculpture, the fine arts, Iranians abroad, and cultural events 
in the Islamic and Western world as reported by the IRNA 
representative offices abroad and from the mass media that 
conform to the tastes of those interested in the arts, culture, 
and literature. 

</TEXT>

