  PAYAM-E KETABKHANEH [the library's message]: (Pamphlet): 
License holder: Ministry of Culture and Islamic Guidance; 
editor in chief: Mohammad Ebrahim Ansari Lari; headed by 
council of writers; most of its contents are centered around 
cultural, literary, and art activities and in introducing the 
latest writings in these fields. 
