<F P=100> Morocco </F>
<H3> <TI>   Fes University Closed After Islamists, Leftists Clash </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  LD0202131694 Algiers Radio Algiers Network in Arabic 1200 
GMT 2 Feb 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD0202131694 </F>
<F P=104>  Algiers Radio Algiers Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Arabic </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Fes University was closed today following 
yesterday's confrontations between Moroccan Islamist students 
and leftists. The security forces surrounded Fes University and 
studies were suspended indefinitely. 
  Similar student confrontations took place in Morocco last 
October, killing one and seriously injuring 10. 

</TEXT>

</DOC>

<DOC>
<DOCNO> FBIS3-34102 </DOCNO>
<HT>    "drnes023_f_94002" </HT>


<HEADER>
<AU>   FBIS-NES-94-023 </AU>
Document Type:Daily Report 
<DATE1>  3 Feb 1994 </DATE1>

