<F P=102>  LD0102174894 Rabat Moroccan Kingdom Radio Network in Arabic 
1600 GMT 1 Feb 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD0102174894 </F>
<F P=104>  Rabat Moroccan Kingdom Radio Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Arabic </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] His Majesty King Hassan II, may God grant him 
victory, has sent the following message of congratulations to 
His Excellency Liamine Zeroual, president of the Republic of 
Algeria: 
  On the occasion of your taking over the presidency of the 
sister Republic of Algeria, we are happy to convey to Your 
Excellency our congratulations and wishes for success in your 
duty. On the same occasion, we wish the fraternal people of 
Algeria further progress, prosperity, and peace. 
  We wish you good health and hope you will kindly accept our 
highest consideration and fraternal esteem. 
  [Signed] Your brother Hassan II, king of Morocco. 

