<F P=102>  LD0402083094 Kuwait KUNA in Arabic 0709 GMT 4 Feb 94 </F>
<F P=103> LD0402083094 </F>
<F P=104>  Kuwait KUNA </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Arabic </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Excerpt] Kuwait, 4 Feb -- The State Security Court will 
tomorrow resume hearings in the case of the terrorist network 
which was intending to assassinate former US President George 
Bush during his visit to Kuwait last year. The plot was 
instigated and planned by the Iraqi intelligence services. 
  On 25 December last year, the court postponed issuing 
sentences in this case in which 11 Iraqi and three defendants 
are implicated and decided to listen again to the main witness. 
[passage omitted -- recapitulation of charges] 

</TEXT>

