<F P=103> JN0302125994 </F>
<F P=104>  Baghdad Republic of Iraq Radio Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Arabic </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Leader President Saddam Husayn has ordered that 
pensioners whose service exceeds 25 years and whose total wages 
and allowances are currently less than 500 dinars be granted an 
additional cost of living allowance totaling 25 percent of his 
monthly wages and allowances. 
  A circular issued by the Presidential Office said that the 
order of the leader president, may God protect him, shall take 
effect as of 1 February. 

