Language: <F P=105> Arabic </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Excerpt] His Majesty King Husayn and Austrian President 
Thomas Klestil held talks in Vienna yesterday. Their 
discussions dealt with bilateral relations and efforts to 
achieve peace in the Middle East. 
  The Austrian president held a dinner banquet in honor of his 
majesty the king. The banquet was attended by top Austrian 
officials. His Majesty King Husayn will hold talks today with 
Austrian Chancellor Franz Vranitzky. 
  His Majesty King Husayn, commander in chief of the Jordanian 
Armed Forces, arrived in Vienna last night, arriving from 
Croatia where he visited the Jordanian troops operating within 
the international peacekeeping forces there. [passage omitted] 

